title: Fantasy Football Statistics: Offense Positions - 2007 Season
name: Fantasy Football Statistics: Offense Positions - 2007 Season
description: This dataset provides statistics on NFL football players for selected offense positions -- quarterback, running back, tight end and wide receiver. Player performance is measured using total fantasy football points for the regular season (www.fftoday.com) and the hometowns of each player geocoded using latitude and longitude coordinates.
